{%- comment -%}
  AI Stylist — App Embed (auto-injects chat bubble on every storefront page).

  Renders nothing when enable_widget is off, so disabling in theme editor
  fully removes the script tag and custom element from the page.

  CSP note: merchants with strict CSP must allowlist
    connect-src https://web-production-3b1d7.up.railway.app
  for the chat fetch. Surfaces in v2 if real merchants hit it.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment -%}
  Agent name duality (007 follow-up): the merchant's preferred agent name
  is set in /app/config (chatAgentName), but the storefront widget can't
  read MerchantConfig directly without an extra fetch on every page load.
  v1 resolution: the theme editor `agent_name_override` below is the
  authoritative source for the storefront. Merchants must set both for now.
  v2 will sync chatAgentName to an app metafield so the widget can read it
  without a fetch — at which point this duality goes away.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if block.settings.enable_widget -%}
  <script>
    window.__AISTYLIST_CONFIG__ = {
      shopDomain: {{ shop.permanent_domain | json }},
      primaryColor: {{ block.settings.primary_color | json }},
      welcomeMessage: {{ block.settings.welcome_message | json }},
      agentName: "{{ block.settings.agent_name_override | default: '' | escape }}",
      chatEndpoint: "https://web-production-3b1d7.up.railway.app/api/chat/message"
    };
  </script>
  <script src="{{ 'chat-widget.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
  <aistylist-widget></aistylist-widget>
{%- endif -%}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "AI Stylist Chat",
  "target": "body",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "enable_widget",
      "label": "Show chat bubble on storefront",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "primary_color",
      "label": "Primary color",
      "default": "#000000"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "agent_name_override",
      "label": "Agent name override",
      "info": "Custom agent name. Leave blank to use the merchant's configured default."
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "welcome_message",
      "label": "Welcome message",
      "default": "Hi! I'm your shopping assistant. How can I help you today?"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
